                picture description not available
            </font></font></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card text-bg-primary mb-3">
            <h3 class="card-header">
                <font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                    <font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">LEGOs</font>
                </font>
            </h3>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">The world of bricks</font></font></h5>
                <p class="card-text"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">I have been building with LEGOs for a very long time, with a major period (2014-2019) where I did it every day. Even though I do it much less often now, LEGO remains a very creative activity that I enjoy. I even participated in a LEGO contest on the Champs-Élysées with 3 friends on September 21, 2025.</font></font></p>
            </div>
            <div class="container-fluid mb-3"> 
                <div class="row g-2">
                    <div class="col-6"> 
                    <br>
                        <img src="/document/lego.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" style="object-fit: cover; height: 250px; width: 100%;" alt="Lego 1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <br>
                        <video class="img-fluid rounded" style="object-fit: cover; height: 250px; width: 100%;" controls>
                            <source src="/document/lego.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        </video>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <img src="/document/lego2.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" style="object-fit: cover; height: 250px; width: 100%;" alt="Lego 3">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <img src="/document/légo.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" style="object-fit: cover; height: 250px; width: 100%;" alt="Lego 4">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer text-bg-primary"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                LEGO contest on the Champs-Élysées, September 21, 2025
            </font></font></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-bg-primary mb-3">
            <h3 class="card-header">
                <font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                    <font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">Video Games</font>
                </font>
            </h3>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">Like the majority of young people, I enjoy playing video games.</font></font></h5>
                <p class="card-text"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">I play games like Brawl Stars, Minecraft, Minecraft Dungeons, Among Us, etc.</font></font></p>
            </div>
            <br>
            <video class="img-fluid rounded" style="object-fit: cover; height: 200px; width: 100%;" controls>
                <source src="/document/bs.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            </video>
            <div class="card-footer text-bg-primary"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font dir="auto" style="vertical-align: inherit;">
                clip from the game Brawl Stars
            </font></font></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>
</div>
